Chapter 1: Project Introduction
Project Name

AI Restaurant Ordering Website Using Flask + Gemini + Voiceflow + Replit

1. Project Overview

Many restaurants still receive customer orders through phone calls or manual WhatsApp messages. This approach can lead to delayed responses, missed orders, and extra work for staff.

In this project, we will build an AI-powered restaurant website where customers can chat with an AI assistant to:

View the menu
Get food recommendations
Ask about prices
Check restaurant timings
Place an order
Share delivery details

The chatbot will use Gemini AI to answer customer questions naturally and Flask to manage the backend logic.

2. Problem Statement

Many restaurants face challenges such as:

Manual order taking
Long customer waiting time
Missed phone calls
Repeated questions about menu and prices
Manual customer record management

These issues reduce customer satisfaction and increase staff workload.

3. Proposed Solution

Develop an AI-powered restaurant website where:

Customers visit the website.
They interact with an AI chatbot.
The chatbot answers questions using Gemini AI.
Customers can place orders.
Customer details and orders are stored automatically.
4. Real-Time Example

Imagine a customer visits Food Paradise Restaurant.

Customer:

Show today's special.

AI:

Today's Specials:

🍕 Veg Pizza – ₹250

🍔 Chicken Burger – ₹180

🥤 Fresh Lime Juice – ₹80

Customer:

Recommend something under ₹300.

AI:

I recommend:

🍔 Chicken Burger

🥤 Fresh Lime Juice

Customer:

I want to order.

AI:

Please provide your Name, Phone Number, and Delivery Address.

The order is then stored for the restaurant staff.

